/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />回你都廢事了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出街問吓人, &quot;學&quot;粤語定英文難啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n知唔知英文生字多幾多, 文法變化多幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係叫一個英文同粵語都唔識嘅人去學依兩種語言<br />\n一定係粵語難學好多 <br />\n<br />\n或者咁講<br />\n英文係易學難精<br />\n粵語係難學難精"},{"pid":"499e6af4c9a4b969fdf172262fc8f2e8ae263041","tid":217772,"uid":56299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"用緊粵語嘅人口都好多 如果真係你口中所講咁撚難 早就跟住一啲稀有方言消失 唔會流傳到今日"},{"pid":"c9ea5269e4faeeb614aa1aa0e45b812f9dbd500d","tid":217772,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的確係<br />\n好似新加坡咁加強英文教育先可以保持競爭力</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知點解要加強蝗語嘅語言地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑到最後一定係英文"},{"pid":"75235b6586f99fcae575de6fd5257dbec43daad8","tid":217772,"uid":34623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:18:46.000Z","msg":"48歲(粵語好難)"},{"pid":"00aa578a59efe3bf4344820045c11dfaa828d6dd","tid":217772,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"抵你破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b4113037261e078118f8c8c417047eab7bd0b7","tid":217772,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:26:10.000Z","msg":"全球過億人講緊粵語, <br />\n香港更加係主流語言 粵語/廣東話既大本營 佔九成<br />\n歷史上有好多語言/文字就真係淘汰左啦<br />\n但點解粵語仲廣泛用緊, 唔係因為難唔難既問題<br />\n係好唔好用既問題, 而且係中原正音, 只係現今北方主流用胡語, 滅粵語, <br />\n你先覺得粵語應該淘汰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93